00:02:04.368 --> 00:02:05.568
You know this, right?

19
00:02:06.167 --> 00:02:07.178
I do.

20
00:02:08.708 --> 00:02:10.747
All the criminal psychology research students...

21
00:02:11.208 --> 00:02:12.377
are members of this club.

22
00:02:13.407 --> 00:02:14.477
Kang Chi Hwan.

23
00:02:15.947 --> 00:02:18.947
You committed murder according to the postings...

24
00:02:19.287 --> 00:02:20.787
on the fan fiction website.

25
00:02:21.187 --> 00:02:22.187
Come on.

26
00:02:22.918 --> 00:02:24.227
Don't be like this.

27
00:02:24.527 --> 00:02:25.988
Don't be like an amateur.

28
00:02:26.858 --> 00:02:29.058
Maybe other people practiced...

29
00:02:29.298 --> 00:02:32.428
