32
00:02:40.808 --> 00:02:42.178
Murder practice?

33
00:02:43.377 --> 00:02:44.447
Isn't that website...

34
00:02:45.747 --> 00:02:47.148
really interesting?

35
00:02:49.018 --> 00:02:50.648
When I read from it,

36
00:02:51.588 --> 00:02:53.958
my fingers start to tingle,

37
00:02:54.787 --> 00:02:55.958
and sometimes...

38
00:02:56.558 --> 00:03:00.027
I feel like I'm actually committing murder.

39
00:03:03.257 --> 00:03:04.727
Don't you want to know...

40
00:03:06.697 --> 00:03:07.937
what it feels like...

41
00:03:10.298 --> 00:03:11.608
to kill someone?

42
00:03:13.608 --> 00:03:17.078
People will die eventually.

43
00:03:19.078 --> 00:03:22.618
Why do I have to waste my time...

44
00:03:22.947 --> 00:03:24.947
for people who are already dead?

45
00:03:26.148 --> 00:03:28.217
He's not nervous at all.

46
00:03:29.157 --> 00:03:32.727
He's aware that there's no clear evidence to prove his murder.

47
00:03:32.787 --> 00:03:33.898
If this continues,

48
00:03:34.527 --> 00:03:37.067
he'll be transferred to prosecutors for special injury.

49
00:03:38.268 --> 00:03:41.738
We don't have an excuse keep him here.

50
00:03:44.537 --> 00:03:48.437
Gather photos and documents of every victim.

51
00:03:48.507 --> 00:03:49.638
Yes, sir.

52
00:03:50.447 --> 00:03:52.108
Kang Chi Hwan's a first offender.

53
00:03:53.007 --> 00:03:54.947
If he feels intimidated by the surrounding,

54
00:03:55.618 --> 00:03:57.817
he'll feel pressured psychologically.

55
00:04:22.137 --> 00:04:23.478
Do you remember this student?

56
00:04:24.007 --> 00:04:25.707
You two studied the same major,

57
00:04:26.007 --> 00:04:27.418
but she was recently murdered.

58
00:04:33.988 --> 00:04:35.288
We operated...

59
00:04:35.587 --> 00:04:38.187
a mystery club called...

60
00:04:38.488 --> 00:04:39.988
"Journal Holmse".

61
00:04:40.827 --> 00:04:44.197
I found her cute, but then she got so clingy,

62
00:04:44.968 --> 00:04:46.728
so I stopped seeing her.

63
00:04:48.137 --> 00:04:49.197
By the way,

64
00:04:49.598 --> 00:04:51.267
who killed her?

65
00:05:00.278 --> 00:05:01.918
That's Ko Joon Hee we talked about earlier.

66
00:05:03.147 --> 00:05:04.887
She's the first victim of the incident.

67
00:05:05.348 --> 00:05:07.788
She was electrocuted with a stun gun,

68
00:05:08.118 --> 00:05:11.058
abducted, tortured,

69
00:05:12.058 --> 00:05:13.457
and abandoned at the end...

70
00:05:13.798 --> 00:05:15.028
like a piece of garbage.

71
00:05:17.567 --> 00:05:19.197
(Body found near Sin Mok Stream)

72
00:05:19.197 --> 00:05:20.668
She's a victim of shooting incident.

73
00:05:26.038 --> 00:05:29.238
There's a narrowing construction area near Nadeulmok.

74
00:05:30.007 --> 00:05:31.408
If you want to get on the outer road,

75
00:05:31.408 --> 00:05:33.817
you must pass this narrow road.

76
00:05:35.747 --> 00:05:37.418
When the man selects a target,

77
00:05:37.988 --> 00:05:40.317
he slows down on purpose...

78
00:05:41.017 --> 00:05:43.058
and blocks the woman's path.

79
00:05:43.728 --> 00:05:47.298
The car behind gets upset, so she comes up,

80
00:05:47.298 --> 00:05:49.358
then the man doesn't miss the chance...

81
00:05:49.358 --> 00:05:51.627
and shoots the gun like this!

82
00:05:55.868 --> 00:05:58.808
Did I get anything wrong?

83
00:05:59.908 --> 00:06:02.978
The order of the crime, pattern, method,

84
00:06:02.978 --> 00:06:04.077
