85
00:06:05.647 --> 00:06:06.978
It's all perfect.

86
00:06:10.548 --> 00:06:12.918
How did you find the culprit's signature?

87
00:06:13.187 --> 00:06:14.187
Pardon?

88
00:06:15.457 --> 00:06:18.158
It's all in the fan fiction.

89
00:06:19.528 --> 00:06:21.158
I only repeated it.

90
00:06:21.397 --> 00:06:24.397
It sounds like you're admitting your crime.

91
00:06:27.298 --> 00:06:30.937
I think I told you earlier that I'm smart.

92
00:06:34.108 --> 00:06:35.608
Do you have any more questions?

93
00:06:40.817 --> 00:06:42.278
You dimmed the light...

94
00:06:43.447 --> 00:06:45.247
