107
00:07:33.798 --> 00:07:36.437
He took the same lectures with Ko Joon Hee,

108
00:07:36.437 --> 00:07:37.937
and they joined the same club.

109
00:07:38.267 --> 00:07:40.067
They're administrators of the fan fiction club.

110
00:07:40.778 --> 00:07:43.308
Above all, on the day the murder notice was posted,

111
00:07:43.377 --> 00:07:46.147
he abducted Son Na Kyung as what's written in the posting.

112
00:07:46.507 --> 00:07:48.218
Do we still need more evidence?

113
00:07:48.377 --> 00:07:51.548
Without a conclusive evidence, we can't imprison him for murder.

114
00:07:51.548 --> 00:07:53.187
The problem is...

115
00:07:53.817 --> 00:07:55.757
the website closed down...

116
00:07:55.757 --> 00:07:57.788
because the information leaked.

117
00:07:58.288 --> 00:08:01.327
I can't trace the club members anymore.

118
00:08:01.428 --> 00:08:03.798
I'm sure they moved the website...

119
00:08:04.067 --> 00:08:05.997
instead of closing it.

120
00:08:06.528 --> 00:08:08.238
Now that he's on it again,

121
00:08:09.098 --> 00:08:11.137
he'll never stop.

122
00:08:20.077 --> 00:08:23.577
(The Night Reaper)

123
