No, I haven't.

127
00:08:58.748 --> 00:09:00.388
- Excuse me. - Yes?

128
00:09:00.418 --> 00:09:02.617
Have you seen this person?

129
00:09:03.617 --> 00:09:05.528
No, I haven't.

130
00:09:25.048 --> 00:09:26.077
Mother.

131
00:09:26.707 --> 00:09:27.847
I...

132
00:09:29.077 --> 00:09:31.447
can't get hold of Seo Young for two days now.

133
00:09:31.687 --> 00:09:32.687
Yes.

134
00:09:33.758 --> 00:09:36.058
We had a fight preparing for the wedding,

135
00:09:36.258 --> 00:09:38.128
but I could always get hold of her.

136
00:09:39.687 --> 00:09:43.258
Don't you think I should tell Father?

137
00:09:43.357 --> 00:09:45.268
We need more time.

138
00:09:46.768 --> 00:09:49.038
I know what you mean,

139
00:09:49.168 --> 00:09:52.607
but solving the case is more important than justifying oneself.

140
00:09:58.977 --> 00:10:00.378
Trust me.

141
00:10:00.477 --> 00:10:02.248
I will solve this.

142
00:10:08.187 --> 00:10:11.357
We have some breaking news. We're shocked to hear...

143
00:10:11.357 --> 00:10:14.128
that during the chase that happened in the middle of the town...

144
00:10:14.158 --> 00:10:16.597
as NCI was trying arrest a suspect of an abduction case,

145
00:10:16.597 --> 00:10:20.467
three citizens were hit by a car and were hospitalized.

146
00:10:42.587 --> 00:10:44.687
It's like we're on a pilgrimage.

147
00:10:45.558 --> 00:10:47.197
These are the traces of the Reaper.

148
00:10:49.028 --> 00:10:51.628
- This is the place. - Look.

149
00:10:51.628 --> 00:10:55.298
(The Night Reaper)

150
00:10:55.298 --> 00:10:58.408
Guys, isn't this place a little scary?

151
00:10:59.467 --> 00:11:00.508
Really?

152
00:11:17.928 --> 00:11:20.898
These stories were kept secret, but people started adding more to them.

153
00:11:20.998 --> 00:11:23.628
It's hard to find the person who wrote it first.

154
00:11:23.628 --> 00:11:26.298
The original site was closed down, but people are making...

155
00:11:26.498 --> 00:11:28.798
more and more similar websites after this case became well-known.

156
00:11:29.998 --> 00:11:32.737
It seems unlikely that we'd find anything through the internet.

157
00:11:33.268 --> 00:11:36.178
If we can't stop the supporters,

158
00:11:36.577 --> 00:11:39.847
many more of Kang Chi Hwan will appear.

159
00:11:39.977 --> 00:11:41.617
That could be the chaos...

160
00:11:42.617 --> 00:11:44.388
that the Reaper wants.

161
00:11:48.388 --> 00:11:51.388
There have been superiors' orders to abort the investigation.

162
00:11:52.227 --> 00:11:53.587
From now on,

163
00:11:53.587 --> 00:11:57.227
regional investigation unit will be in charge.

164
00:11:57.498 --> 00:11:58.567
All right?

165
00:11:59.327 --> 00:12:02.668
The superiors seem to believe that the fact that NCI is in charge...

166
00:12:02.837 --> 00:12:06.567
could only stimulate the culprits of this case.

167
00:12:06.967 --> 00:12:10.778
As you may already know, the public already has a negative view...

168
00:12:10.778 --> 00:12:12.347
on this team, and it could worsen.

169
00:12:12.548 --> 00:12:15.977
Chief Director Baek, the Reaper is after us.

170
00:12:16.178 --> 00:12:19.187
Are you asking us to step out in such a situation?

171
00:12:19.388 --> 00:12:21.087
This is an order, so proceed accordingly.

172
00:12:22.288 --> 00:12:23.658
Do you understand, Team Manager Kang?

173
00:13:08.097 --> 00:13:10.808
What? On Chief Manager Baek?

174
00:13:25.487 --> 00:13:27.457
Team Manager Kang, you should take a look at this.

175
00:13:27.717 --> 00:13:29.717
Someone uploaded a strange writing on the bulletin board.

176
00:13:29.857 --> 00:13:30.888
Here.

177
00:13:30.888 --> 00:13:32.158
(NCI Bulletin Board)

178
00:13:33.558 --> 00:13:35.128
(The woman was looking at a building with so many windows.)

179
00:13:40.638 --> 00:13:42.337
(NCI Bulletin Board)

180
00:13:42.538 --> 00:13:44.107
Someone could be...

181
00:13:45.308 --> 00:13:47.378
leaving us a message.

182
00:13:50.707 --> 00:13:52.808
(The woman was looking at a building with so many windows.)

183
00:13:54.018 --> 00:13:56.748
"The woman was looking at a building with so many windows."

184
00:13:57.347 --> 00:13:58.687
"I will die here."

185
00:13:58.788 --> 00:14:00.888
"If possible, I want it to be today."

186
00:14:01.758 --> 00:14:04.357
"I hope you are the one that kills me."

187
00:14:06.158 --> 00:14:07.928
I think the style has gotten a little different.

188
00:14:07.998 --> 00:14:11.028
Until now, the stories have directly described the murders.

189
00:14:11.197 --> 00:14:14.138
But this one is indirectly predicting a murder.

190
00:14:16.798 --> 00:14:20.067
A woman who is asleep. A drowsy sunlight.

191
00:14:21.808 --> 00:14:23.477
