192
00:14:24.808 --> 00:14:27.617
And there are passersby and a bus stop.

193
00:14:28.977 --> 00:14:30.717
People without facial expressions.

194
00:14:31.317 --> 00:14:34.918
Team Manager Kang, near the bus stop 271,

195
00:14:35.058 --> 00:14:36.957
there's a department store with a clock tower.

196
00:14:37.357 --> 00:14:40.087
In front of the store, there's a crosswalk and an intersection.

197
00:14:47.538 --> 00:14:50.567
It's describing the road we were hiding to catch Kang Chi Hwan.

198
00:14:52.808 --> 00:14:53.937
The Reaper.

199
00:14:55.437 --> 00:14:57.178
This must be the Reaper's writing.

200
00:14:58.678 --> 00:15:00.977
Son Na Kyung is hospitalized at Seojin Hospital.

201
00:15:01.447 --> 00:15:02.477
Yes.

202
00:15:04.388 --> 00:15:07.258
Team Manager Kang, I found out where the chief director is.

203
00:15:07.957 --> 00:15:09.258
He's at Seojin Hospital.

204
00:15:16.558 --> 00:15:19.227
The number you have dialed is not available at this moment.

205
00:15:20.067 --> 00:15:21.768
The chief director is not answering my calls.

206
00:15:39.288 --> 00:15:40.518
Where am I supposed to go to?

207
00:16:02.908 --> 00:16:05.808
What do you want me to do?

208
00:16:06.178 --> 00:16:08.778
Why? Are you disappointed...

209
00:16:09.447 --> 00:16:11.317
