210
00:16:12.388 --> 00:16:13.788
Where is she?

211
00:16:14.388 --> 00:16:16.258
If you really want to see her,

212
00:16:17.227 --> 00:16:18.857
I'll let you see her.

213
00:16:42.477 --> 00:16:43.617
How do you like it?

214
00:16:44.048 --> 00:16:46.548
Now, if you want to save your daughter,

215
00:16:47.487 --> 00:16:49.418
