216
00:16:52.327 --> 00:16:53.327
What's wrong?

217
00:16:53.857 --> 00:16:56.957
Isn't your family the one thing that you are afraid of losing?

218
00:16:57.567 --> 00:16:59.597
If you want something from me, let's meet up.

219
00:17:00.898 --> 00:17:01.967
Please.

220
00:17:02.837 --> 00:17:04.237
Don't do anything to her.

221
00:17:04.808 --> 00:17:06.768
