222
00:17:09.837 --> 00:17:11.407
Gosh, you guys.

223
00:17:12.147 --> 00:17:15.847
Why is everything so complicated with you guys?

224
00:17:17.117 --> 00:17:18.917
Your family is dying.

225
00:17:19.847 --> 00:17:21.288
To save your daughter,

226
00:17:22.188 --> 00:17:23.587
kill her.

227
00:17:24.188 --> 00:17:25.357
Kim Yong Chul,

228
00:17:26.127 --> 00:17:28.228
