229
00:17:28.657 --> 00:17:31.728
If you just do as I tell you, I'll let your daughter go.

230
00:17:33.667 --> 00:17:35.097
You have only once chance.

231
00:17:37.407 --> 00:17:38.768
Do you see the drawer?

232
00:17:41.137 --> 00:17:42.337
Open it.

233
00:17:55.887 --> 00:17:57.188
Pick the scalpel up.

234
00:18:03.498 --> 00:18:04.597
You know what to do.

235
00:18:08.667 --> 00:18:12.038
Don't hesitate, and kill her at once.

236
00:19:15.567 --> 00:19:17.867
Son Na Kyung. Son Na Kyung.

237
00:19:19.667 --> 00:19:21.407
I called the Chief Director's house...

238
00:19:21.407 --> 00:19:23.438
