254
00:21:02.107 --> 00:21:03.677
Don't think about doing anything stupid.

255
00:21:05.248 --> 00:21:06.248
Kang Ki Hyung.

256
00:21:06.808 --> 00:21:09.478
Your pet is rather noisy.

257
00:21:09.617 --> 00:21:12.718
