259
00:21:17.887 --> 00:21:21.458
Let's see if I can just walk out of this room in 10 minutes or not.

260
00:21:43.147 --> 00:21:44.248
Kim Yong Chul,

261
00:21:44.917 --> 00:21:46.317
I understand your pain.

